Description: You can use Energy Melee to power your blows with pure energy. These focused power attacks often Disorient opponents. Like all Stalker primary attack powers, Energy Melee attacks can land a Critical Hit for double damage, if you are properly Hidden or if your target is Slept or Held.

Powers.DescShort: Melee, Moderate DMG(Smash/Energy), Foe Disorient, Special
Powers.DescLong: You perform a quick punch that deals moderate damage. Coupled with other energy punches, Barrage can Disorient a foe. This power will have a 100% chance to stun and weaken the target's secondary effects and regeneration rate if used while in Energy Focus mode. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Fast
You perform a powerful Energy Punch that deals moderate damage. When used with other Energy Melee attacks, Energy Punch can Disorient your opponent. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Fast
This melee attack deals a good amount of damage and has a good chance to Disorient the target. Damage: High, Recharge: Moderate

A signature Stalker attack.  This attack does superior energy and smashing damage on its own as a frontal attack and cannot be interrupted.  However, if it is executed while you are Hidden, this attack will do tremendous damage, as you waylay your unsuspecting foe. This attack may be interrupted if you move or are attacked while executing this power and are hidden.  Using this power while not hidden has a chance to critically hit equal to 33.3% times the number of stacks of Assassin's Focus. Using Assassin's Strike when not hidden will remove all stacks of Assassin's Focus regardless if you critically hit or not.  Damage: Special, Recharge: Slow
Greatly increases the amount of damage you deal for a few seconds, as well as slightly increasing your chance to hit.  Recharge: Long

Allows you to trick a foe to no longer attack you.  A Successful Placate will also Hide you.  This Hide is very brief, and offers no Defense bonus, but it will allow you to deliver a Critical Hit or an Assassins Strike. However, if you attack a Placated Foe, he will be able to attack you back. Recharge: Long

Powers.DescShort: Melee (Cone), Moderate DMG(Smash/Energy), Foe Disorient, Special
Powers.DescLong: You focus your internal energy on your fists, and release it once you hit your target uneashing an energy wave that hurts and disorients multiple enemies. This power will hit up to 5 additional foes if used while in Energy Focus mode. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Moderate

Powers.DescShort: Melee, Extreme DMG(Energy/Smash), Foe Disorient, +Energy Focus
Powers.DescLong: Total Focus is complete mastery over Energy Melee. This melee attack is a very slow, but incredibly devastating attack that can knock out most opponents, leaving them Disoriented. Due to the exhausting nature of Total Focus, recharge time is very long. This power will enter Energy Focus mode. Total Focus Criticals do not result in double damage, instead it grants double Energy Focus. Damage: Extreme, Recharge: Slow

Powers.DescShort: Melee, Extreme DMG(Energy), Foe Disorient, Self -HP, Special
Powers.DescLong: Mastery of Energy Melee culminates with the ability to transfer your own Hit Points into a punch that deals extreme damage. Energy Transfer has a good chance of Disorienting the target. This power will execute extremely quickly if under Energy Focus mode. Damage: Extreme, Recharge: Moderate
